Xi optimistic about China's economic fundamentals
              
Digg
  Source: Xinhua | 2016-01-18 21:42:17 | Editor: huaxia
BEIJING, Jan. 18, 2016 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Xi Jinping speaks at a symposium attended by ministers and provincial officials in Beijing, capital of China, Jan. 18, 2016. (Xinhua/Li Xueren)
BEIJING, Jan. 18 (Xinhua) -- Despite downward growth pressure and recent financial market volatility, President on Monday said that the country's long-term economic fundamentals remain sound.
